Installation Instructions
-------------------------


Dependencies
-----------------------

qt4-dev (must have qt version 4.4 or greater, 4.4 is available in hardy-backports)
libsqlite3-dev
cmake (this is the build system used, verion 2.4 or greater)
libginac-dev
libgsl0-dev (version 1.9 or greater)
libboost-dev C++ libraries (only use shared_ptr.hpp)

Build and run instructions
----------------------------

1. run cmake
2. run make
3. execute ark3d


Example build and run process
------------------------------------

cmake .
make
./src/Interface/ark3d



